data.description: This super sweet home checks all the boxes for charm, location and amenities. Situated on almost four acres, with an in-ground swimming pool, pond and community access to the Hiwassee River. The three bedroom, two full bathroom and two half bath home boasts the Master Suite on the main floor, with French Door access to the covered and screened porch overlooking the fenced pool area and the en-suite bathroom has both a shower and separate jetted tub. Additional French Doors lead out to the porch from the living and dining area, giving the whole room a bright and cheery feel. The custom kitchen features granite counter tops and leads to a separate laundry room with pantry.    Upstairs features a bonus room, second full bathroom and two additional bedrooms with closets and extra storage space. The basement features a small kitchenette with a half bath and Rec Room which leads to the one car garage. Outside you will find mature landscaping surrounding the house and the large in-ground pool. Just a short walk will take you to the common area on the Hiwassee River for fishing or tubing. Plenty of additional parking is available for you and your guests, because you will definitely want to entertain friends and family here!
